 of Medieval and Early Modern culture<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Cultural responses to economic change<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Representations of political dissent and rebellion<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Utopias and dystopias<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Gender, sexuality, and social change<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><b>Deadline:<\/b>\u00a0 A conference proposal and a short biography to\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:derrick.higginbotham@uct.ac.za\" target=\"_blank\">derrick.higginbotham@uct.ac.za<\/a>\u00a0<b>by 30 November 2015<\/b>.\u00a0 Any inquires can be directed to the same email address.<\/p>\n<p>The CFP has been posted to our website at\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/sasmarsnewsletter.blogspot.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">http:\/\/sasmarsnewsletter.<wbr \/>blogspot.com\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Call for Papers Southern African Society for Medieval and Renaissance Studies Conference 26 \u2013 28th\u00a0August, 2016 &nbsp; We are pleased to announce that the 23rd\u00a0biennial conference of SASMARS will be held at Mont Fleur in Stellenbosch, South Africa on 26 \u2013 28th\u00a0August 2016. \u201cTexts and Transformations: Medieval and Early Modern Cultures\u201d Medieval and Early Modern [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[3],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.codl.nl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1299"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.codl.nl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.codl.nl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.codl.nl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.codl.nl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1299"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https:\/\/www.codl.nl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1299\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1308,"href":"https:\/\/www.codl.nl\/wp-js